1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 4=

3
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:18,239
Young Master Luo,
you're a man of status.

4
00:00:18,239 --> 00:00:19,839
Why would you go to the Gate Bureau

5
00:00:19,839 --> 00:00:20,760
to be a lowly constable?

6
00:00:21,079 --> 00:00:22,199
Wouldn't it be better

7
00:00:22,199 --> 00:00:24,320
to enjoy yourself
in this den of pleasure?

8
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,760
That's where you're wrong.

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,839
(Luo Wuxia, son of the Luo family)
As the only male heir of the Luo family,

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,800
I was destined

11
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,800
to be the world's greatest constable.

12
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,560
What would a lady like you know?

13
00:00:33,079 --> 00:00:35,679
But I recall you don't
know any martial arts, Master Luo.

14
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,320
Money is all I need, isn't it?

15
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:40,190
Is there anything
that money can't solve?

16
00:00:40,479 --> 00:00:41,679
If it can't be solved,

17
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,679
it just means you didn't pay enough.

18
00:00:48,712 --> 00:00:51,350
(Hu Lie, the Black Twister)

19
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,679
What now?

20
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,240
Robbing me?

21
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,240
Fine.

22
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,280
You can take everything in the back.

23
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,519
But listen up.

24
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:07,079
You can take the money,

25
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:10,040
but do not delay me
from reporting to the Gate Bureau.

26
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,799
The Gate Bureau?

27
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,280
I hate constables the most.

28
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,280
Since you're a lackey
of the Gate Bureau,

29
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:19,200
you're meeting your end today!

30
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,000
Take him!

31
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,640
How dare you!

32
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,079
Do you know who I am?

33
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:25,079
Who my sister is?

34
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,239
Who my grandfather is?

35
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:27,480
He is the Commissioner...

36
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:28,319
Get down from there!

37
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:28,959
of the Bureau!

38
00:01:35,375 --> 00:01:38,000
(Black Gale Abode)

39
00:01:45,462 --> 00:01:47,512
(Wanted Poster)

40
00:01:50,787 --> 00:01:53,637
(Honor as Vast as the Heavens)

41
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:56,920
(Luo Wushuang,
Deputy of the Gate Bureau)

42
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,170
So, you are the Black Twister.

43
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,519
Who are you?

44
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,239
Since the 10th year of Wanli,

45
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,000
you have ruled Black Gale Abode,

46
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,599
robbing countless merchants.

47
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,640
You hijacked official silver three times
and abducted twenty-one women.

48
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,319
Sister!

49
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:10,680
With 133 lives on your hands,

50
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,000
do you plead guilty?

51
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,800
Since you know my record so well,

52
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,759
you still dare to come here alone?

53
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:23,000
Aren't you afraid
of being eaten alive here?

54
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,719
Who is the lamb and who is the tiger?

55
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,319
That remains to be seen.

56
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:29,000
Kill her!

57
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,837
(Honor as Vast as the Heavens)

58
00:02:45,837 --> 00:02:47,350
(Wanted Poster)

59
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,319
Luo Wushuang, Deputy
of the Gate Bureau's Field Corps,

60
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,490
reporting back to headquarters.

61
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,100
(Commissioner Luo Shixun)

62
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,120
(Commissioner Luo Shixun)
My respects, Commissioner.

63
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,319
Shuang, you're back.

64
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,680
Grandfather.

65
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:18,039
You led the team that rescued Wuxia

66
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,680
and wiped out Black Gale Abode.

67
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,560
The Personnel Corps has
decided to commend you.

68
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,390
You've been promoted by three ranks.

69
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,120
Thank you, Commissioner.

70
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,000
Where is Wuxia?

71
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,000
Did he not return with you?

72
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,240
You'll have to wait for him.

73
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,100
He said that riding was too tiring,

74
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,879
so he insisted on
coming back by carriage.

75
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,120
It'll be a few more days.

76
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,439
Grandfather,

77
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,240
why did you

78
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,319
summon me back?

79
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,439
A private matter.

80
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,120
A private matter?

81
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,360
What is it?

82
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:50,639
I've arranged a blind date for you.

83
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,080
A blind date?

84
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:57,639
Dad, you know that Chang is
the only one I want to marry.

85
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,319
And yet...

86
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,599
Just listen to who it is

87
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,919
before you make a decision.

88
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,800
I don't care.

89
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,520
Even if she were the princess herself,

90
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,639
I wouldn't be interested.

91
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,960
It's Wushuang.

92
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,520
Who?

93
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,159
Luo Wushuang.

94
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,360
Don't worry, Chang.

95
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,879
I won't let you down.

96
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,000
What's wrong?

97
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:48,040
Are you taking back
the gift you gave me?

98
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,079
I never said I was taking it back.

99
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,110
I was just worried it'd be uncomfortable

100
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,800
while you were trying to sleep.

101
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,680
This is my "painkiller."

102
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:59,199
I need to hold on to it.

103
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,879
Chang, I'm so sorry.

104
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,240
My family did this to you.

105
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,759
I'm the one who should be saying sorry.

106
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:13,879
If my uncle hadn't offended
the wrong people in business,

107
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:17,240
your sister and I
wouldn't have been kidnapped.

108
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,639
Lately,

109
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,399
I've been thinking about us.

110
00:05:24,050 --> 00:05:25,879
I believe that
for two people to be together,

111
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,240
sincerity comes first.

112
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,519
There shouldn't be secrets between us.

113
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,639
So...

114
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:40,000
Buyu, I...

115
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,120
Chang, you're right.

116
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:44,079
There should be
no secrets in a relationship.

117
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:45,839
That's why I need to apologize.

118
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,319
I need to be honest with you.

119
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,000
I...

120
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,000
Tell me.

121
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:56,879
I...

122
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,710
My father is trying to set me up
with Luo Wushuang.

123
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,759
Who is that?

124
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,079
She's our Commissioner's granddaughter.

125
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,079
But please, don't worry.

126
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,920
Wushuang and I have been
like siblings since we were kids.

127
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:19,279
Besides, she's incredibly proud.

128
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:21,639
There's no way
she'd ever be interested in me.

129
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,439
Trust me.

130
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,240
I'll make sure to settle this

131
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,460
and explain everything to her.

132
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,680
Otherwise, my dad will keep meddling.

133
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,519
Is this what you wanted to tell me?

134
00:06:33,650 --> 00:06:34,639
Don't get the wrong idea.

135
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,360
You're the only one in my heart.

136
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,439
You silly man.

137
00:06:38,620 --> 00:06:39,680
You've told me the truth,

138
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,120
so how could I misunderstand?

139
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,120
You really are the best.

140
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,600
All right, Chang.

141
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,519
You're recovering.

142
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,480
You need to rest.

143
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,480
Come now.

144
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,959
Get some sleep.

145
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,160
I'll stay right here with you.

146
00:07:19,662 --> 00:07:20,183
Stop!

147
00:07:26,975 --> 00:07:29,712
(Lady Thousand-Hands, Lin Xin'er)

148
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,439
Fellow traveler, state your business.

149
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:36,959
Leave the cart, and you live.

150
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,040
Lady,

151
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:40,399
this belongs to the Sihai Escort.

152
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:56,720
Queen Thief of the South,
Lady Thousand-Hands!

153
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:09,920
Move out.

154
00:08:17,362 --> 00:08:18,321
To the Capital.

155
00:08:19,012 --> 00:08:21,411
It's time to meet the leader
of the Martial Alliance...

156
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:25,600
The Sacred Hand Sect.

157
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,680
Waiter! Bring some wine!

158
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,920
Coming right up!

159
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,679
Buyu,

160
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:35,480
do you know why

161
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,440
we are meeting today?

162
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,799
I heard our elders

163
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,799
wanted to set us up.

164
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:46,159
They certainly put
a lot of thought into this.

165
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:47,919
Shuang,

166
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,559
we're like brothers.

167
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:51,399
You couldn't possibly
be interested in me.

168
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,480
Waiter! Over here!

169
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,559
Coming!

170
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,320
If I weren't interested,

171
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,399
I wouldn't have come.

172
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,190
Then, stop drinking.

173
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,919
You should just eat.

174
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,879
Have some of this.

175
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,440
Buyu!

176
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,680
- Auntie!
- What a coincidence!

177
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,039
You're here too?

178
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,879
Buyu, who is this?

179
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:19,919
Buyu,

180
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:22,039
since when did your taste
become so poor?

181
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,240
How can you just sit here

182
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:25,399
chatting and eating with just any woman?

183
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:27,679
What did you say?

184
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,679
What did I say?

185
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:29,559
Did I say something?

186
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,679
I barely opened my mouth,

187
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,840
and you're already snapping.

188
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,039
How terrifying!

189
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:34,679
Little girl, listen up.

190
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,320
Being this nasty

191
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:38,200
will only scare the men away.

192
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,759
You... I...

193
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,919
Looking at it this way,

194
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,399
our Chang really is the best.

195
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,679
- She's refined and cultured.
- Chang...

196
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,759
And understanding too.

197
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:50,320
No wonder you're determined to marry her.

198
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,320
Wait, Shuang...

199
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,120
This is my fiancée's aunt.

200
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,320
She didn't mean it like that.

201
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,200
Oh, but I did.

202
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:02,559
I just can't stand seeing people

203
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:04,039
act all lonely and desperate.

204
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,639
Tell you what,

205
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,919
I'll have Auntie Yun arrange

206
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,960
dozens of men for you to meet.

207
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,840
That way, you won't have any time left

208
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,559
to cling to other people's fiancés!

209
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,000
Auntie!

210
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,559
Look, they are having a quarrel.

211
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,320
What's going on?

212
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,039
No idea.

213
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:19,960
Auntie, you should really eat something.

214
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,320
Just a few bites, Auntie.

215
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,279
Why are you still sitting here?

216
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,320
Go find Chang!

217
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,480
Yu.

218
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,759
Since you already have a fiancée,

219
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,279
why did you agree to meet me?

220
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,720
Wushuang,

221
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,279
this meeting

222
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,320
was my father's idea.

223
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,399
But I also wanted to make things clear.

224
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,279
There is no future for us.

225
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,990
If I have caused offense,

226
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,200
please forgive me.

227
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,279
Why don't you two finish the meal?

228
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,480
I'll take my leave.

229
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,480
I'm leaving too.

230
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,559
Buyu!

231
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,840
Until we meet again, lady!

232
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:53,919
Wushuang, take your time.

233
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:54,919
I've settled the bill.

234
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,480
Enjoy.

235
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:04,480
(Cuiyun Restaurant)
Scented sachets and pendants!

236
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,679
Not bad, Mao Buyu.

237
00:11:05,810 --> 00:11:07,890
You went behind Chang's back
to have a blind date.

238
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,120
With a female Deputy, no less.

239
00:11:09,130 --> 00:11:10,279
Auntie, you've got it all wrong.

240
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:11,279
I don't have

241
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,559
romantic feelings for Wushuang.

242
00:11:12,559 --> 00:11:13,399
I can swear to it.

243
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,320
Drop the act.

244
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,120
If you're so brave,

245
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,480
go explain yourself to our Chang.

246
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:19,480
I told her about this.

247
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,750
I was just on my way to see her.

248
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:21,919
I'll take my leave now.

249
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:35,600
I'll only say one thing.

250
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:37,200
Chu Yunchang is my niece.

251
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,519
Keep your hands off her man.

252
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:41,080
And if I refuse?

253
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,279
Then, let me give you a little tip.

254
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,639
A lantern in a latrine

255
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,960
can bring death.

256
00:11:47,325 --> 00:11:48,625
(Cuiyun Restaurant)

257
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,799
Nimbus Palm!

258
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,404
You're from the Sacred Hand Sect!

259
00:12:00,225 --> 00:12:00,825
Let's go!

260
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:05,214
A Plum Blossom Dart...

261
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,799
The King of Thieves!

262
00:12:08,575 --> 00:12:09,216
(What?)

263
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:11,919
(The Sacred Hand Sect
and the King of Thieves are)

264
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:12,890
(backing Chu Yunchang?)

265
00:12:19,350 --> 00:12:22,625
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

266
00:12:22,663 --> 00:12:25,538
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

267
00:12:26,038 --> 00:12:31,756
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

268
00:12:32,938 --> 00:12:36,258
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

269
00:12:36,388 --> 00:12:39,308
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

270
00:12:40,476 --> 00:12:45,716
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

271
00:12:46,938 --> 00:12:49,331
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

272
00:12:49,331 --> 00:12:52,981
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

273
00:12:53,050 --> 00:12:56,540
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

274
00:12:56,638 --> 00:12:59,613
♪To the ends of time♪

275
00:12:59,613 --> 00:13:02,988
♪The moon traces your face♪

276
00:13:03,175 --> 00:13:06,763
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

277
00:13:06,763 --> 00:13:13,003
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

278
